OL,3,CNesbitt: Health service reform 'about
OL,4,Cmore than reconfiguring hospital
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FThe reform of health and social care
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland is about more than
OL,9,Freconfiguring hospital services,
OL,10,FStormont's Health Minister has said.
OL,12,FMike Nesbitt was speaking ahead of a
OL,13,Fspeech by the expert who led a major
OL,14,Freview in reforming Northern Ireland's
OL,15,Fhealth service in 2016.
OL,17,FThe plan announced by Professor Rafael
OL,18,FBengoa was never fully implemented
OL,19,Famid the collapse of two assemblies
OL,20,Fand the Covid-19 pandemic.
