OL,7,FMr Nesbitt said he hopes Prof Bengoa's
OL,8,Fspeech will help "refocus attention on
OL,9,Fwhat needs to be done."
OL,11,FProfessor Bengoa will speak at a
OL,12,Fconference later today.
OL,14,FHe said he had invited the health
OL,15,Fpolicy expert back to Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fas one of his first initiatives after
OL,17,Ftaking on the Stormont ministry in May
OL,18,Fin order to "reboot the reform agenda
OL,19,Fand to provide his assessment of what
OL,20,Fneeds to be done."
