OL,3,CNesbitt: Health service reform 'about
OL,4,Cmore than reconfiguring hospital
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,F"Systems Not Structures was about much
OL,8,Fmore than our hospitals. It's about
OL,9,Ffundamentally rebalancing provision to
OL,10,Fprovide more care at community level,
OL,11,Fto focus on prevention rather than
OL,12,Ftreatment, and to help people manage
OL,13,Fconditions and live long healthy
OL,14,Flives," he said.
OL,16,F"Reconfiguring hospital services
OL,17,Fremains an important part of the
OL,18,Foverall jigsaw, as I emphasised last
OL,19,Fweek when I launched the Hospitals `
OL,20,FCreating A Network For Better Outcomes
OL,21,Fdocument for public consultation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@GO]xD@AOU
