OL,3,CNesbitt: Health service reform 'about
OL,4,Cmore than reconfiguring hospital
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,F"I have also on many occasions
OL,8,Fstressed that improving population
OL,9,Fhealth and tackling health
OL,10,Finequalities are among my key areas of
OL,11,Ffocus.
OL,13,F"We can only hope to achieve this, and
OL,14,Fdeliver meaningful reform, if we adopt
OL,15,Fa whole-government approach with
OL,16,Fsupport right across the Executive,
OL,17,Fthe wider public sector, our
OL,18,Fcommunities and our clinicians."
