OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of his address,
OL,8,FProfessor Bengoa said he welcomes the
OL,9,Fopportunity to see how health
OL,10,Ftransformation remains an overriding
OL,11,Fpriority in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,F"I am, of course, very aware of the
OL,14,Fchallenges Northern Ireland's health
OL,15,Fservice has faced over the period
OL,16,Fsince 2016," he said.
OL,18,F"It is by no means unique in that
OL,19,Fregard. Right across Europe, there are
OL,20,Fmajor struggles on a number of fronts.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@LO]zD@AOU
