OL,3,CNesbitt: Health service reform 'about
OL,4,Cmore than reconfiguring hospital
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,F"These include balancing short term
OL,8,Fpressures with long term reform needs,
OL,9,Fdealing with growing demand and
OL,10,Fgreater patient complexity, and
OL,11,Frecovering from the impact of the
OL,12,FCovid-19 pandemic.
OL,14,F"The analysis in Systems Not
OL,15,FStructures is just as valid today as
OL,16,Fwhen it was published and the need for
OL,17,Ftransformation, backed by sustained
OL,18,Fresources, is ever more pressing."
